  "technicalDetails": "<p>Features:</p><ul><li><strong>Movement. </strong>There is a jumping system, as well as a system for movement in running and walking states. A combat system is also available, where it is possible to walk in a fighting stance in all directions, while making dashes or dodging an attack, etc ...</li><li><strong>Health component</strong>. This component comprises all parameters of health. It can be used not only with the character, but with any <strong>actor</strong>, which might need health parameters.</li><li><strong>Melee Weapon</strong>. The class of melee weapon for close quarters combat.</li><li><strong>AI</strong>. Basic AI is capable of hearing, seeing, following, and attacking the player from short range.</li><li><strong>XP management component.</strong> The component comprises all necessary logic to handle leveling up of a character.</li><li><strong>Game Interface (HUD). </strong>There is a fully animated game interface.</li><li><strong>Combat overview</strong>. A cinematic camera in combat.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Number of Blueprints: 33</p><p>Input: Keyboard, Mouse</p><p>Network Replicated: No</p><p>Documentation:<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/0Byd53EBIW1D8RnNzeWx3MVozQWs/view?usp&#61;sharing&amp;resourcekey&#61;0-mVLW6xAewWmQ4bgXw4GnhQ\" rel=\"nofollow\">Eng</a> (The package is completely compatible with the package &#34;CloseCombat:Swordsman&#34;.)</p><p>Important/Additional Notes: <strong>Attention, there are no sounds in the project.</strong> All the exiled presented in the video are including locations, characters, effects and cutscenes</p><p>Online support: <a href=\"https://discord.gg/FvhuKAm\" rel=\"nofollow\">Discord channel</a></p><p>Animations:</p><p>Number of Animations: 287</p><p>Scaled to Epic skeleton: Yes</p>",
